title: Don’t call me a madman
description: Don’t call me a madman Manhua The Sacred Gate of Heaven is established, and the fabric of time and space twists within the mortal realm. When the earth gives birth to twelve celestial landscapes, and the moon no longer belongs to humanity… where will we go? The world of gods? The realm of demons? No, this is the world of humans! I will wear the crown that no one can shatter and become the king of a new era. My name is Ren Jie! Born to rise above, destined to conquer. 别叫我恶魔, Don’t Call Me A Devil
